Amazon MQ:
==========
- opensource message broker.
- managed apachee activeMQ
- compatible with JMS API or protocol such as AMQP, MQTT
- can function as a queue or topic.
- one-to-one or many-to-many (i.e it can function as a SNS or SQS)
- to open the active mq web console, make sure that port 8162 is open in the security groups.
- SNS & SQS using amazon proprietary services. so if you want to migrate the existing message service to amazon then we have to user "Acitve MQ"


MQ Components:
broker
  - single instances
  - Highly available pair (active/standby)
  - managed updates.
